{"tid":1120722,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"［的士狗］屌你老母過海收來回隧道費。","createTime":"2019-04-23T00:31:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-23T05:31:26.000Z","uid":35092,"like":69,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"54e7fba99180ecb8e0e872d2f9abdaec30934d26","tid":1120722,"uid":35092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T00:31:19.000Z","msg":"屌你老母，過海要比來回隧道費，我都算。<br />\n<br />\n你老母，轉個頭係香港又接一個去九龍，話自己係香港車，又收來回隧道，你咪好好賺？！來回過一次隧道，你老母收四次隧道費！<br />\n<br />\n好啦，我當你架的士去排過海的士站，你係咪唔收人隧道費先？唔係啊嘛！你咪一樣收人一程隧道費！換句說話講，來回一次隧道，你收左三次隧道費！<br />\n<br />\n所以收來回隧道費係極度不合理條例！我搭幾錢，我咪比幾錢囉！我做乜要包埋你返去果程？！我包埋同你老婆上床好唔好？！<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母的士狗 ！"},{"pid":"7cf52827425e270f4a50e875e61bd1e9a8b58b02","tid":1120722,"uid":130445,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T00:45:19.000Z","msg":"又有道理"},{"pid":"46a243b101c285534bcb1e968739c12382cffa71","tid":1120722,"uid":90020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T01:09:04.000Z","msg":"唔比咪得"},{"pid":"0c3b7ed6ce64767cc959f70119069b8fee520676","tid":1120722,"uid":9230,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T01:27:55.000Z","msg":"即係你究竟算定唔算呀??<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3a473c91b07e36fdd29159b389656d9bdb8123d","tid":1120722,"uid":51105,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T01:28:38.000Z","msg":"唔係過海站截嘅的士係要俾來回費<br />\n但只係$10同$15<br />\n斷估你唔會咁撚on9行西隧俾足$65個司機掛？"},{"pid":"62914b4cb471c18fc9257f59b8688150a6c11803","tid":1120722,"uid":51105,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"b3a473c91b07e36fdd29159b389656d9bdb8123d","tid":1120722,"uid":51105,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T01:28:38.000Z","msg":"唔係過海站截嘅的士係要俾來回費<br />\n但只係$10同$15<br />\n斷估你唔會咁撚on9行西隧俾足$65個司機掛？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T01:31:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mVehUjT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmVehUjT